and not the other way around,

497
00:38:04,958 --> 00:38:07,875
you don't get to do
any "strongly advising."

498
00:38:07,958 --> 00:38:09,791
I'm on your side, Ivan.

499
00:38:09,875 --> 00:38:12,791
