the, uh, shark attacks to a minimum.

500
00:38:13,375 --> 00:38:15,625
Well, in that case,
maybe you should do your job.

501
00:38:15,708 --> 00:38:17,541
Get those kids off the street

502
00:38:17,625 --> 00:38:21,458
